    ],
    charactersEn: [
      'Odin, the All-Father who sacrificed himself for the runes and his eye for wisdom',
      'Yggdrasil, the world tree upon which Odin hung for nine nights',
      'Gungnir, Odin\'s enchanted spear that pierced his own side',
      'Mimir, guardian of the well of wisdom who demanded Odin\'s eye',
      'Huginn & Muninn, Odin\'s pair of ravens, "Thought" and "Memory"',
